senses.sense_definition: Consisting of, or limited to, letters and/or numbers, especially the characters A to Z and 0 to 9.

examples.text: Please create a secure password that contains at least one <w>alphanumeric</w> character.
The serial number on the device is an <w>alphanumeric</w> code.

senses.sense_definition: Consisting of letters, numbers, and occasionally punctuation or other special characters.

examples.text: The system needs to process complex <w>alphanumeric</w> data that includes symbols.
This field accepts <w>alphanumeric</w> strings with special formatting.

senses.sense_definition: A character that is either a letter or a number.

examples.text: The software filters out symbols and keeps only the <w>alphanumerics</w>.
He typed a random string of <w>alphanumerics</w> into the terminal.
